  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\n\nThe warning message for not sending real ETH on testnet runs off the screen on Oneplus 6T on the Send Transaction screen.\n\n#### Expected behavior\n\nWarning message should wrap nicely\n\n#### Actual behavior\n\nWarning message runs half a character off screen before wrapping.\n\n#### Acceptance Criteria\n\nWarning message wraps correctly.\n\n### Reproduction\n\n- Open Status\n- Login to app and change network to Ropsten test network\n- Go to wallet and select account\n- Tap send \n- Note warning message runs off screen\n\n### Additional Information\n\n- Status version: Develop Branch - 10/10 build\n- Operating System: Android\n- Device - Oneplus 6T\n\n#### Logs\n![Screenshot_20191014-203929](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17355484/66791793-a3768e00-eec3-11e9-90a3-3d95b17fcb09.jpg)",
